name: Ethernium Golden Doge
description:
"Fear of man will prove to be a snare, but whoever trusts in the Lord is kept safe. Fearing people is a dangerous trap, but trusting the Lord means safety. The fear of man lays a snare, but whoever trusts in the Lord is safe."

This  shows the relationship of the veneration of the golden calf in ancient times with our new forms of idols within the digital memeplex.

Part of MoMO (Museum Of Modern Objkt) 2021. @boreuno
